{
  "description": "A vibrant and expansive nighttime scene showcases a fireworks display over a city skyline and a long bridge extending into dark waters. The fireworks are a dazzling burst of white, red, and blue, creating a bright focal point against the dark sky. Beneath the fireworks, the city is illuminated with numerous lights, forming a glittering urban landscape. A prominent bridge, featuring glowing lights along its length, stretches horizontally across the foreground. The water is dark and reflects some of the city lights, creating a shimmering effect. The overall composition presents a dynamic contrast between the explosive energy of the fireworks and the static, orderly arrangement of the city and bridge.",
